 />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明果班功夫佬係超級系<br />\n無啦啦加幾個正常人落場都唔知做乜鳩<br />\n最後咪又係俾主角屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e373996f3d4e16b94833b8fa3a94c6e35109756","tid":310572,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有碧咸 朗拿度 拖丹</blockquote><br />\n係碧蠶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明果班功夫佬係超級系<br />\n無啦啦加幾個正常人落場都唔知做乜鳩<br />\n最後咪又係俾主角屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小順、古烈治（王小妹專用）<br />\n功夫隊隊長兼前鋒<br />\n唐大順之弟<br />\n功夫：唐家十二路彈腿<br />\n暗戀王小妹，最後為其男友<br />\n患有恍惚症，因此對功夫、足球和王小妹以外的記憶過目即忘，而且病發時更會一動不動，最後痊癒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後加盟西甲皇家馬德里。代表中國足球隊上陣超過七十場，帶領中國隊奪得兩次世界盃冠軍，而且也為效力的歐洲球隊帶來四次歐冠冠軍，個人五次勇奪歐洲金靴獎和連續三次獲得世界足球先生。身價是全球最高。</span><br />\n與林中虎亦師亦友<br />\n林中豹、朴迪路之天敵<br />\n黃風之對手兼天敵<br />\n招式：哈雷彗星大S射球、彈腿第十式&middot;萬腿穿心、玄音盾、彈腿終極絕招&middot;千鈞勢 鳥斂翼 天雨石"},{"pid":"37ed4af64bd116a4819e9846d8a54145f6356814","tid":310572,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好耐無見</blockquote><br />\n係 呢排少左上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲係係咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b3260853d921f6728bbb85238713c19aa5de09","tid":310572,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有碧咸 朗拿度 拖丹</blockquote><br />\n係碧蠶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明果班功夫佬係超級系<br />\n無啦啦加幾個正常人落場都唔知做乜鳩<br />\n最後咪又係俾主角屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小順、古烈治（王小妹專用）<br />\n功夫隊隊長兼前鋒<br />\n唐大順之弟<br />\n功夫：唐家十二路彈腿<br />\n暗戀王小妹，最後為其男友<br />\n患有恍惚症，因此對功夫、足球和王小妹以外的記憶過目即忘，而且病發時更會一動不動，最後痊癒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後加盟西甲皇家馬德里。代表中國足球隊上陣超過七十場，帶領中國隊奪得兩次世界盃冠軍，而且也為效力的歐洲球隊帶來四次歐冠冠軍，個人五次勇奪歐洲金靴獎和連續三次獲得世界足球先生。身價是全球最高。</span><br />\n與林中虎亦師亦友<br />\n林中豹、朴迪路之天敵<br />\n黃風之對手兼天敵<br />\n招式：哈雷彗星大S射球、彈腿第十式&middot;萬腿穿心、玄音盾、彈腿終極絕招&middot;千鈞勢 鳥斂翼 天雨石</blockquote><br />\n講緊林保怡用晒成副身家請大哨佢地踢一場波喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a553115dc6bc97b7d0fa1a59477015206eea1732","tid":310572,"uid":29202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有碧咸 朗拿度 拖丹</blockquote><br />\n係碧蠶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明